&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage your experience to optimize the portfolios of our investors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with internal data teams to create visibility into operational performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Derive insights from operating performance aimed at enhancing NOI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform high volume rent underwriting analysis on new and existing portfolio properties&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide input on the asset management playbook&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop an in-depth understanding of institutional partners and produce outcomes aligned with their goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and track budgets and budget to actual trend analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead regional market meetings and goal setting that drive performance that focuses on occupancy, renewal performance, turn performance, and service trends for various regions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide input and development on process SOPs that are used by cross functional teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor the performance of recently acquired assets and influence future&amp;nbsp; acquisitions by providing data driven insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete hold sell analysis for low or troubled performing assets on a periodic basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise the Buying Team on market trends, real estate opportunities and buy box strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement inventory and revenue management strategies&lt;/li&gt;
