&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Month end close:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the month-end close process to ensure timely and accurate financial reporting. This involves overseeing the entire cycle from pre-close preparation and journal entry management to balance sheet reconciliations and flux analysis.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Implementation:&lt;/strong&gt; You will champion our AI-first approach by integrating AI agents to streamline and automate journal entries, reconciliations, and variance reporting, ensuring that month-end is not just a deadline, but an efficient, insight-driven process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Accounting:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage complex technical accounting areas, including stock-based compensation (ASC 718), lease accounting (ASC 842), capitalized software costs (ASC 350-40), and M&amp;amp;A purchase accounting (ASC 805)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consolidation: &lt;/strong&gt;Lead the monthly financial consolidation process for a complex structure of multiple legal entities, ensuring accurate intercompany eliminations and strict compliance with GAAP standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Reporting:&lt;/strong&gt; Drive the velocity and precision of monthly, quarterly, and annual reporting cycles.&amp;nbsp;Produce our monthly financials including the cash flow statement. Transform variance analysis into proactive insights that guide executive decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ERP Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Design and implement an ERP strategy to optimize our financial platforms.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Audit: &lt;/strong&gt;Lead the annual financial statement audit, acting as the primary liaison for external auditors. Oversee the preparation and review of complex financial statement footnotes to ensure full GAAP compliance. Proactively manage the audit lifecycle, including detai

