&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Receiving and interacting with visitors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Answering and managing incoming calls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining paper and online records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitoring and organizing Executive’s inboxes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Providing other daily support as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform accounts payable processing and other basic accounting functions as needed to include:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handling expense accounts and reimbursements via Coupa&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with entering and processing approved payments as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining detailed files/records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle confidential and sensitive information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide backup office management support as needed (weekly lunch orders, supplies, office POC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be available to support the executives outside of normal business hours as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
